                                <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2509Weddas">Wǝddāse Māryām</title>
                                <textLang mainLang="gez"/>
                                
                                <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.3.1">
                                    <locus from="209r"/>
                                    <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2509Weddas#Monday">Wǝddāse Māryām: : Monday</title>
                                    <incipit xml:lang="gez"><seg type="inscriptio">ውዳሴሃ፡ ለእግዝእትነ፡ ማርያም፡ ዘይትነበብ፡ በዕለተ፡ ሰኑይ፡</seg> ፈቀደ፡ እግዚእ፡ ያግዕዞ፡ ለአዳም፡ ኅዙነ፡ ወትኩዘ፡ ልብ፡</incipit>
                                </msItem>
                                
                                <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.3.2">
                                    <locus from="210r"/>
                                    <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2509Weddas#Tuesday">Wǝddāse Māryām: : Tuesday</title>
                                    <incipit xml:lang="gez"><seg type="inscriptio">ውዳሴ፡ ዘሠሉስ፡</seg> አክሊለ፡ ምክሕነ፡ ወቀዳሚተ፡ መድኃኒትነ፡</incipit>
                                </msItem>
                                
                                <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.3.3">
                                    <locus from="211v"/>
                                    <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2509Weddas#Wednesday">Wǝddāse Māryām: : Wednesday</title>
                                    <incipit xml:lang="gez"><seg type="inscriptio">ውዳሴ፡ ዘረቡዕ፡</seg> ኵሉ፡ ሠራዊተ፡ መላእክት፡ ይብሉ፡ ብፅዕት፡ አንቲ፡</incipit>
                                </msItem>
                                
                                <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.3.4">
                                    <locus from="213v"/>
                                    <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2509Weddas#Thursday">Wǝddāse Māryām: : Thursday</title>
                                    <incipit xml:lang="gez"><seg type="inscriptio">ውዳሴ፡ ዘሐሙስ፡</seg> ዕፀ፡ እንተ፡ ርእየ፡ ሙሴ፡ በነደ፡ እሳት፡ ውስተ፡ ገዳም፡</incipit>
                                </msItem>
                                
                                <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.3.5">
                                    <locus from="215v"/>
                                    <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2509Weddas#Friday">Wǝddāse Māryām: : Friday</title>
                                    <incipit xml:lang="gez"><seg type="inscriptio">ውዳሴ፡ ዘዓርብ፡</seg> ቡርክት፡ አንቲ፡ እምአንስት፡</incipit>
                                </msItem>
                                
                                <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.3.6">
                                    <locus from="217r"/>
                                    <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2509Weddas#Saturday">Wǝddāse Māryām: : Saturday</title>
                                    <incipit xml:lang="gez"><seg type="inscriptio">ውዳሴ፡ ዘቀዳሚት፡ ሰንበት፡</seg> ንጽሕት፡ ወብርህት፡ ወቅድስት፡ በኵሉ፡
                                    እንተ፡ ሐዋፈቶ፡ ለእግዚእ፡ በእራኃ፡</incipit>
                                </msItem>
                                
                                <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.3.7">
                                    <locus from="218r"/>
                                    <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2509Weddas#Sunday">Wǝddāse Māryām: : Sunday</title>
                                    <incipit xml:lang="gez"><seg type="inscriptio">ውዳሴ፡ ዘእኁድ፡</seg> ተሰመይኪ፡ ፍቅርተ፡ ኦቡርክት፡ እምአንስት፡</incipit>
                                </msItem>
                            </msItem>
                            
                            <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.4">
                                <locus from="219v"/>
                                <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1113Anqasa">ʾAnqaṣa bǝrhān</title>
                                <textLang mainLang="gez"/>
                                <incipit xml:lang="gez"><seg type="inscriptio">ውዳሴ፡ ወግናይ፡ ዘእግዝእትነ፡ ማርያም፡</seg> ቅድስት፡ ወብፅዕት፡ ስብሕት፡ 
                                ወቡርክት፡ ክብርት፡ ወልዕልት፡ አንቀጸ፡ ብርሃን፡ ማዕርገ፡ ሕይወት፡ ወማኅደረ፡ መለኮት፡ ቅድስተ፡ ቅዱሳን፡ አንቲ ውእቱ፡ ኦእግዝእትነ፡ ማርያም፡ ድንግል፡ 
                                ወላዲተ፡ አምላክ።</incipit>
                            </msItem>
                            
                        </msItem>
                        
